descriptionHtml:
Chickens need a Rooster like in real life this mod add 30 roosters in 29 places Riverwood,Rorikstead,Farms,Markath Exteriors Etc...is a small mod for immersion.

Installation Simple drag and drop or via NMM.

highly recommended mod Roosters At Dawn http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17257/?
